Class ToDoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ToDoList
  • public class ToDoList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is part of the ToDo application. ToDo is a very simple, text based todo list application. This class holds a list of tasks objects. Users can add, remove tasks.
